tool_input.script:
export const meta = {
  name: 'qa-semantic-search',
  description: 'Execute semantic search for QA workflow',
  phases: [
    { title: 'SemanticSearch', detail: 'Search knowledge files for relevant sections' }
  ]
}

phase('SemanticSearch')
const result = await agent(
  `Execute the semantic search workflow defined in workflows/semantic-search.md.

The working directory is: /home/tie303177/work/nabledge/work2/.claude/skills/nabledge-6

Query: "バッチ処理の進捗状況をWebSocketでリアルタイムにブラウザへ通知したい。NablarchでWebSocketを使う方法はあるか？（処理方式: ウェブアプリケーション）（目的: 実装したい）"

Steps to follow:
1. Read the file workflows/semantic-search.md in the working directory
2. Execute it step by step with the query above
3. For each page candidate, explain why it was selected or skipped
4. For each section, explain why it was selected (high/partial) or skipped

Return a JSON object with this structure:
{
  "selected_pages": [{"path": "<path relative to knowledge/>", "reason": "<why selected>"}],
  "excluded_pages": [{"path": "<path relative to knowledge/>", "reason": "<why skipped>"}],
  "selected_sections": [
    {"file": "<full file path>", "section_id": "<sN>", "relevance": "<high|partial>", "reason": "<why selected>"}
  ],
  "excluded_sections": [
    {"file": "<full file path>", "section_id": "<sN>", "reason": "<why skipped>"}
  ]
}`,
  {
    label: 'semantic-search',
    phase: 'SemanticSearch',
    schema: {
      type: 'object',
      properties: {
        selected_pages: {
          type: 'array',
          items: {
            type: 'object',
            properties: {
              path: { type: 'string' },
              reason: { type: 'string' }
            },
            required: ['path', 'reason']
          }
        },
        excluded_pages: {
          type: 'array',
          items: {
            type: 'object',
            properties: {
              path: { type: 'string' },
              reason: { type: 'string' }
            },
            required: ['path', 'reason']
          }
        },
        selected_sections: {
          type: 'array',
          items: {
            type: 'object',
            properties: {
              file: { type: 'string' },
              section_id: { type: 'string' },
              relevance: { type: 'string', enum: ['high', 'partial'] },
              reason: { type: 'string' }
            },
            required: ['file', 'section_id', 'relevance', 'reason']
          }
        },
        excluded_sections: {
          type: 'array',
          items: {
            type: 'object',
            properties: {
              file: { type: 'string' },
              section_id: { type: 'string' },
              reason: { type: 'string' }
            },
            required: ['file', 'section_id', 'reason']
          }
        }
      },
      required: ['selected_pages', 'excluded_pages', 'selected_sections', 'excluded_sections']
    }
  }
)

return result
